[idols] cannot speak!”","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2548.mp3","surahId":21,"words":[{"id":57156,"position":1,"arabic":"ثُمَّ","translation":"এরপর","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57157,"position":2,"arabic":"نُكِسُوا۟","translation":"অবনত হয়ে গেলো","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57158,"position":3,"arabic":"عَلَىٰ","translation":"ওপর","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_003.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57159,"position":4,"arabic":"رُءُوسِهِمْ","translation":"তাদের মস্তকগুলোর","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_004.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57160,"position":5,"arabic":"لَقَدْ","translation":"\"(এবং বলল) নিশ্চয়ই","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_005.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57161,"position":6,"arabic":"عَلِمْتَ","translation":"তুমি জেনেছো","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_006.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57162,"position":7,"arabic":"مَا","translation":"না","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_007.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57163,"position":8,"arabic":"هَـٰٓؤُلَآءِ","translation":"এরা সব","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_008.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57164,"position":9,"arabic":"يَنطِقُونَ","translation":"কথা বলতে পারে\"","audioUrl":"wbw/021_065_009.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57165,"position":10,"arabic":"٦٥","translation":"(৬৫)","audioUrl":null,"charTypeName":"end"}]},{"number":66,"arabic":"قَالَ أَفَتَعْبُدُونَ مِن دُونِ ٱللَّهِ مَا لَا يَنفَعُكُمْ شَيْـًۭٔا وَلَا يَضُرُّكُمْ","translation":"Said [Abraham]: “Do you then worship, instead of God, something that cannot benefit you in any way, nor harm you?","audio":"https://cdn.islamic.network/quran/audio/128/ar.alafasy/2549.mp3","surahId":21,"words":[{"id":57680,"position":1,"arabic":"قَالَ","translation":"সে বললো","audioUrl":"wbw/021_066_001.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57681,"position":2,"arabic":"أَفَتَعْبُدُونَ","translation":"\"কি তবুও তোমরা ইবাদাত করবে","audioUrl":"wbw/021_066_002.mp3","charTypeName":"word"},{"id":57682,"po